00:19:14,380 --> 00:19:16,760
Hey! Over here!


308
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:18,210
Warrior!


309
00:19:30,210 --> 00:19:32,220
Such a great slab of meat.


310
00:19:42,490 --> 00:19:43,550
What's going on?


311
00:19:43,640 --> 00:19:45,510
They must be shy with strangers?


312
00:19:45,630 --> 00:19:48,330
Soldiers and civilians combined,
there is a total of...


313
00:19:48,470 --> 00:19:50,280
3, 4, 5, 6 survivors.


314
00:19:50,900 --> 00:19:53,950
They are also wounded.
Will they be all right?


315
00:19:54,260 --> 00:19:55,510
Yes, I think so.


316
00:19:55,950 --> 00:20:00,730
I just absorbed some magic
from the monster's blood to refill my MP.


317
00:20:00,840 --> 00:20:02,380
Is that possible?


318
00:20:02,670 --> 00:20:05,080
I heard that a bandit
turned into a Berserker


319
00:20:05,320 --> 00:20:09,550
by ingesting too much monsters' meat.


320
00:20:10,030 --> 00:20:12,480
So I thought,
we should be able to absorb magic.


321
00:20:13,470 --> 00:20:15,540
You could have told us sooner.


322
00:20:15,690 --> 00:20:18,660
No, this is also the first time
I've tried it.


323
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:19,930
Warriors.


324
00:20:20,820 --> 00:20:23,790
Thank you very much.
We're very grateful.


325
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:24,620
You're welcome.


326
00:20:25,080 --> 00:20:27,450
Who are you?
Where are you going?


327
00:20:28,030 --> 00:20:30,640
We're soldiers from the Deock Empire.


328
00:20:31,090 --> 00:20:36,020
We have an order from the King
to transfer the pagans to Radorpo.


329
00:20:37,240 --> 00:20:39,690
